metadata.dc:description: Review of two new cases of fracture of the cavernous body, one treated with early surgery and the other one conservatively. In both cases, the patients preserved good erections after one year.
metadata.dc:title: Rotura de cuerpos cavernosos: aportación de dos nuevos casos.
[Rupture of the cavernous body: report of 2 new cases].
